        <h1>Durham </h1>
        
        <p> The Summer School 2021 will be hosted at Durham University, in the North of England. Durham is a small, picturesque city famous for its cathedral and castle. Lectures will be held on the University's Science Site, and accommodation will be in Hatfield College. The city is easily accessible by train (on the East Coast Main Line) or by car via the A1. </p> 
        
        <p> There are no lectures or events planned for Wednesday afternoon, allowing for plenty of time to explore the city. </p>
                
